'''Iliria College''' (''Iliria Royal University'', [[Albanian language|Albanian]]: ''Kolegji Iliria'') is a private provider of higher education in [[Kosovo]]. The Iliria Kolleg Pristina began its activity in 2001 as a private institution which combines the Albanian educational tradition with contemporary concepts.<ref>[http://www.uiliria.org/en/university/ui Webinformation Iliria Royal University]</ref> The Iliria College is member of the [[Balkan Universities Network]].
As of 2013, it is accredited by the ''Kosovo Accreditation Agency'' to offer courses in computer science, business, and law.
