'''Yangon Planetarium''' is a [[planetarium]] located in [[Myanmar]]'s capital city, [[Yangon]]. It presents a half-hour star show illuminated against the planetarium's domes ceiling.<ref>http://yangonlife.com.mm/en/directory/planetarium YangonLife</ref> The building was donated by the government of [[Japan]] in 1987. On the grounds, there is also a 70s-era [[Myanma Airways]] plane exhibited a walk-thru exhibit.<ref>http://www.mmbiztoday.com/articles/guide-yangon-s-museums MMB</ref>
